                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 130rb: Purchase note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ወጳጳስሂ፡ አቡነ፡ ቄርሎስ፡ ወአስበ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ፲ወ፫፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ኢይፃእ፡ ኀበ፡ ካልእ፡ ሀገር፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ፩አላባ፡ ውዝዝ [sic]፡ ውእቱ።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">The Metropolitan is ˀabunä Qerəllos. The payment for the book is 13 (Bərr). This book may not be taken out to another place except wrapped in a wripping; this is forbidden.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 130rb: Note prohibiting to take the book out without textile secondary cover (?).</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ኢይጻእ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ፩ልብስ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ኢትርስዑኒ፡ ማኅበር፡ ዘደብረ፡ ብርሃን፡ ጊዮርጊስ።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">[Fol. 130rb]: This book may not be taken out except (wrapped in) a vestment; this is forbidden by the authority of Peter and Paul. Do not forget me, the community of Däbrä Bərhan Giyorgis.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Fol. 2v. Exercise in writing: the Trinitarian doxology (incomplete).&#xD;
- Fol. 8v, in the upper margin. Crude note.&#xD;
- Fols. 13r, 39r, Corrections or omissions written in the upper margin.&#xD;
- Some portions of the text (mainly kǝśtätat) are written in compressed script (s. fols. 30vb–31rb, 49vb–50ra, 54rb–54va, etc.).</item>
                     </list>
